---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <section id="about" class="pt-32 pb-24 bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-900/40 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center flex flex-col items-center">
        <p class="reveal text-xs font-medium text-accent tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">About me</p>
        <h1 class="reveal d1 font-display font-bold text-5xl md:text-6xl text-zinc-900 dark:text-white leading-tight mb-8">Engineering with purpose,<br>researching with precision.</h1>
        
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-12">
          <p class="reveal d2">
            I'm Shahbaz Fareed, an AI & ML Researcher and Software Engineer based in Islamabad, Pakistan. I hold a Bachelor of Science in Computer Science from Bahria University.
          </p>
          <p class="reveal d3">
            I specialize in architecting intelligent systems, from enterprise-grade RAG pipelines to real-time computer vision solutions. My work bridges the gap between complex mathematical research and robust, deployable software.
          </p>
          <p class="reveal d4">
            Currently, I'm focused on advancing Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) strategies and optimizing deep learning models for real-time edge processing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal d5 w-full pt-12 border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800">
          <p class="text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Stack &amp; expertise</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3" role="list" aria-label="Skills">
            <span role="listitem" class="stag bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 px-5 py-2 rounded-full hover:border-accent transition-colors">Python</span>
            <span role="listitem" class="stag bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 px-5 py-2 rounded-full hover:border-accent transition-colors">PyTorch</span>
            <span role="listitem" class="stag bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 px-5 py-2 rounded-full hover:border-accent transition-colors">LangChain</span>
            <span role="listitem" class="stag bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 px-5 py-2 rounded-full hover:border-accent transition-colors">RAG & LLMs</span>
            <span role="listitem" class="stag bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 px-5 py-2 rounded-full hover:border-accent transition-colors">Flutter</span>
            <span role="listitem" class="stag bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 px-5 py-2 rounded-full hover:border-accent transition-colors">Docker & Podman</span>
            <span role="listitem" class="stag bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 px-5 py-2 rounded-full hover:border-accent transition-colors">SQL & Vector DB</span>
            <span role="listitem" class="stag bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-700 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 px-5 py-2 rounded-full hover:border-accent transition-colors">Flask</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>